                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250113-174-off920 t18250113-174-cd921"></join>, a pair of trowsers, value 3 s.; a hat, value 20 s., and a handkerchief, value 6 d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
